fehd.ADR_TC: 香港中環砵典乍街16號太富商業大廈地下

result.adr_address: 10 Pottinger St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: SUSHI NAKAMOTO （鮨 中本）

reviews.text: This place is giving me a taste of decent Japanese restaurant exactly like I am at Japan. The chef is very concentrated on making good food for the guests. I appreciate his attitude a lot. Also, the food and decorations. Very nice dining experience!

Very nice Japanese Sushi restaurant!!!
The environment is great and the food is awesome! The price is a bit high but the quality of the food definitely speaks for it!!! So impressed with the whole dining experience. The uni and toro are my favourite! So tasty and so good! It's actually my first time trying out OMAKASE, and I will absolutely come back for it!
authentic Japanese sushi, very good quality but pricey
Great quality lunch
One of the best sushiyas in town. Great quality shari with wide variety of neta, and value for money. Michelin candidate IMO
